	<article class="post-505104 post type-post status-publish hentry category-elections category-financial-services category-legal tag-commodity-futures-trading-commission tag-democratic-party-org-republican-party-org tag-derivatives tag-elections tag-intrade tag-nadex tag-north-american-derivatives-exchange tag-president-obama tag-timothy-g-mcdermott per-obama-barack des-derivatives-financial-instruments des-elections des-futures-and-options-trading des-presidential-election-of-2012 des-regulation-and-deregulation-of-industry org-commodity-futures-trading-commission nyt_request_org-north-american-derivatives-exchange" id="post-505104">
	<header class="postHeader">
